    {
      "id": "PopularPost209741",
      "post_content": "It really drove me nuts that all of those \"inflatable\" cards back then (this one, Firebreathing, etc.) didn't say \"until end of turn\" on them. They had plenty of room - Blessing, for example, has to win a prize for smallest amount of card text on a card - and yet they left it off. So, all of us noobs thought we could make the Shade larger permanently turn after turn.\n  \n   \nAs for this card, it's been outclassed over the years, but I still like the name and artwork. Good times...\n  ",
      "posted_by": "Radagast",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost209741\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">It really drove me nuts that all of those \"inflatable\" cards back then (this one, Firebreathing, etc.) didn't say \"until end of turn\" on them. They had plenty of room - Blessing, for example, has to win a prize for smallest amount of card text on a card - and yet they left it off. So, all of us noobs thought we could make the Shade larger permanently turn after turn.\r<br/> <br/>As for this card, it's been outclassed over the years, but I still like the name and artwork. Good times...\r<br/></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '209741'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy42025\">Radagast</span>\r\n                                (11/6/2011 8:22:59 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/Rig